      <title>哥本哈根歷史悠久的證券交易所發生火災，尖塔倒塌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/fire-breaks-out-copenhagens-historic-stock-exchange-spire-collapses-2024-04-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週二，哥本哈根舊證券交易所發生火災，這座丹麥首都最具代表性的建築之一，吞噬了其尖頂，倒塌到屋頂。目前還沒有人員受傷的報告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/fire-breaks-out-copenhagens-historic-stock-exchange-spire-collapses-2024-04-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 07:17:00 GMT</pubDate>
